snippet.title: MYSTERIOUS
snippet.description: Welcome to my channel! I work extremely hard on my videos to give you guys facts & my opinions. I love receipts and I love to bring you guys good quality content that is easy to follow & understand. I stand up for things that I believe is wrong and speak on what is right. Please consider subscribing and let’s have some fun and spill some tea!
